//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
Sony A7S-III Settings

    Memory: CF Express Card
    Format: XAVC S-I (4k)

    Recommended Picture Profiles
        Picture Profile: PP1 (Look flat but better than default)
            Black Level: +2
            Gamma: Movie
            Black Gamma: N/A
            Knee: N/A
            Color Mode: Movie
            Saturation: -2
            Color Phase: 0
            Color Depth: N/A
            Detail
                Level: -2
                Adjust: N/A
    
        Picture Profile: PP6 (Looks natural yet cinematic)
            Black Level: +10
            Gamma: Cine2
            Black Gamma: N/A
            Knee: N/A
            Color Mode: Cinema
            Saturation: -10
            Color Phase: 0
            Color Depth: N/A
            Detail
                Level: +2
                Adjust: N/A
    
        Picture Profile: PP7 (Looks a bit cinematic) - 4k, 1600ISO
            Black Level: 0
            Gamma: S-Log3
            Black Gamma: N/A
            Knee: N/A
            Color Mode: S-Gammut3.Cine
            Saturation: 0
            Color Phase: 0
            Color Depth: N/A
            Detail
                Level: -3 (Day time), -7 (Night shots)
                Adjust: N/A
    
        Picture Profile: PP10 (Cinematic silhouette) - A6600 HLG3 in SDR
            Black Level: 0
            Gamma: HLG3
            Black Gamma: N/A
            Knee: N/A
            Color Mode: BT.2020
            Saturation: 0
            Color Phase: 0
            Color Depth: N/A
            Detail
                Level: N/A
                Adjust: N/A

