Menu Setting

    /////////////////////////
    Camera Icon
        Image Quality
            File Format:
                XAVC S-I (4k) - Recommended: XAVC HS 4k

            Movie Settings
                Rec Frame Rate: 24p
                Record Setting 50M 4:2:0

            Slow and Quick Setting (S&Q)
                Rec Frame Rate: 60p
                Frame Rate: 120fps
                Record Setting 50M 4:2:0

            Proxy
                Proxy Recording: Off
                Proxy File Format: XAVC S-I (4k)
                Proxy Rec. Settings: 16M 4:2:0

        Media >
            Rec. Media Settings
                Prioritize Rec. Media: Slot 1 
                Recording Mode: Simultaneous (Video)
                Auto Switch Media: On
                
        File >
            File Settings
                File Number: Series
                Series Counter Reset
                File Name Format: Standard
                Title Name Settings
            
        Audio Recording>
            Audio Recording: On
            Audio Rec Level: 6 (With Video Mic Go), 25 (With External Mic)
            Audio Out Timing: Live
            Wind Noise: Off
            Shoe Audio Set: -
            Audio Level Display: On (For internal audio recording)

        Image Stabilization >
            SteadyShot: Active
            SteadyShot Adjust: Auto
            Focal Length: -

        Zoom >
            Zoom >
            Zoom Range: Clear Image Zoom (Will crop the video) - Use only with low ISO (good lighting)
            Zoom Speed >
            i Zoom Speed >

        Shooting Display >
            Grid Line Display (Usually for Photo)

        Marker Display
            Marker Display: ON
            Center Marker: Off
            Apect Marker: Off
            Safety Zone: 90%
            Guideframe: On

    /////////////////////////
    +/- Icon (Exposure/Color)
        Metering
            Metering Mode: Multi
            Face Priority in Multi Metering: On (Detect faces and show exposure for their faces)
            Spot Metering Point: Focus Point Link
        White Balance
            White Balance: C.Temp./Filter
            Priority Set in AWB: Standard
            Shockless WB: 2 (Smoothly adjust to white)
        Color/Tone
            D-Range Optimizer: Off
            Creative Look: ST
            Picture Profile: Off
        Zebra Display
            Zebra Display
            Zebra Level: 100+

    /////////////////////////
    AF/MF Icon
        AF/MF
            Focus Mode: Continuous AF
            AF Transition Speed: 4
            AF Subject Shift Sensitivity: 5(Responsive)
        Focus Area
            Focus Area: Zone (Wide / Spot:M)
            Focus Area Limit
            Focus Area Color: White
            Circ of Focus Point: Does not circulate
            AF Frame Move Amt: Standard
        Face/Eye AF
            Face/Eye Prior. in AF: On
            Face/Eye Subject: Human
            Right/Left Eye Select: Auto
            Face/Eye Frame Display: On
            Regist. Faces Priority: On (The camera recognizes target's face among the group)
        Focus Assistant
            Focus Magnification Time: No Limit
            Initial Focus Mag: x4.0

    /////////////////////////
    Playback Icon (Leave as default)

    /////////////////////////
    Network (Leave as Default) - Transfer pictures and not videos
        
