        Reset/Save Settings
            Save/Load Settings (Load custom settings from 3rd parties)
                https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1aJQ37p4yJcvCOnLu4Wfv_8IZOcuEJLLQ
        Finder/Monitor
            Select Finder/Monitor: N/A
            Monitor Brightness: N/A
            Viewfinder Bright: N/A
            Finder Color Temp: N/A
            Viewfinder Magnification: Standard
            Display Quality: High
            Finder Frame Rate: High (Standard = higher battery life)
        Power Setting Option
            Power Save Start Time: 5 min
            Auto Power OFF Temp: High (Lets the camera heat up hotter without auto shut off)


